description:
Noire don't need no help to have some fun in the sun! Grab the Noire Swimsuit Outfit and duke it out with any 2D enemy!

Note: Players can access the Noire Swimsuit Outfit by going to the Menu and scrolling to the Equipment section. The Noire Swimsuit Outfit is purely cosmetic and is visible during battle, cut scenes, and exploration segments with Neptune. Mix-n-match with the animal sets for fun!
name: Noire Swimsuit Outfit
